snippet.title: Sanguivore: Twenty Below - Early Access Official Release [Trailer] [4k]
snippet.description: Immerse yourself in a heart-pounding, first-person multiplayer horror experience that will keep you on the edge of your seat. Gather your courage and team up with up to four friends to brave this escape room-style nightmare. As survivors, your collective objective is to outsmart a gruesome end using every resource at your disposal.
